urlText: Trains run to a changed timetable between South Coast Line stations and the City Circle
content:
Sunday 31 October
  • From 5.50am until 8am, trains run to a changed timetable between South Coast Line stations and the City Circle.
  • T4 Eastern Suburbs & Illawarra Line trains run between Central and Bondi Junction.
  • You may need to change trains at Central or Town Hall to continue your journey.
  • Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date information.
